metadata.name: Taxi, Taxi (的士, 的士) !
metadata.description:
Hailing a taxi is an art form in itself; a quintessential Hong Kong ritual. This is where the daily journey begins for most netizens. 

Specifications: 2580x1935
Tools: Panasonic Lumix GX8, LEICA SUMMILUX 25mm

Collector Perks:  
* A raffle prize: Personal tour with me to these various Hong Kong destination, including an intimate food tour of my favorite cafe diners or the few remaining street stall restaurants 
* A signed Canson Infinity Platine Fibre rag print for each piece collected
* Airdrop gift for each collector and bidder
